headline: Brown & Brown (BRO) Q4 Earnings Beat Estimates
summary: Brown & Brown (BRO) delivered earnings and revenue surprises of +2.53% and -2.16%, respectively, for the quarter ended December 2025. Do the numbers hold clues to what lies ahead for the stock?

headline: AJG Gears Up to Report Q4 Earnings: Here's What to Expect
summary: Arthur J. Gallagher's Q4 results are likely to reflect new business, solid retention, and higher renewal premiums across its segments.
